  The Study
──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  The study is a sanctuary of dark oak panels, where the only illumination comes from a single candelabra flickering against the persistent drumming of autumn rain on the leaded windows. A rich scent of aged leather and extinguished pipe tobacco hangs heavy in the air, casting long, dancing shadows that seem to cling to the room's silent, watchful corners.
